Given that the original description uses "bridgesii" and not "bridgesi", I suspect that is correct and Pilsbry's spelling with a single "i" was incorrect, while Roth & Sadeghian's with two "i"'s is correct. Pilsbry describes it as "at best only a weakly differentiated race of nicklinana" so probably not a huge deal either way.
